      "rationale": "Mean absolute error for relative hemolysis index across five operating points: 8.4%. RMSE: 0.11 (dimensionless RH). Systematic offset attributed to turbulence model underprediction of recirculation zone corrected via SST k-omega model selection. Output comparison meets MRL 2 requirements."
