    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements. Validation results for primary hemolysis index and secondary shear stress distribution support model credibility for CPB worst-case identification use. Decision consequence HIGH acknowledged; medium model influence confirmed by independent bench testing. COU1 credibility assessment accepted for regulatory submission supporting 510(k) predicate comparison.",
